            {
              "_type": "text",
              "text": "Work on content without publishing right away. Alinea makes it easy to manage drafts, archive old pages, and keep your workspace tidy. The workflow stays simple for everyday tasks, but gives you the structure and control needed for larger, more complex projects."
            }
